                    a.btn.btn-primary.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') Empresa
        // About
        section#about.about-section.text-center
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.mx-auto
                        h2.text-white.mb-4 Somos Tausistemas
                        p.text-white-50 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Error voluptas repudiandae provident eum vel! Deserunt rerum quo ipsa quasi vitae eum provident harum corporis, impedit ea dolor iste dicta voluptates.
                img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/ipad.png', alt='')

        // Projects
        section#projects.projects-section.bg-light
            .container
                // Featured Project Row
                .row.align-items-center.no-gutters.mb-4.mb-lg-5
                    .col-xl-8.col-lg-7
                        img.img-fluid.mb-3.mb-lg-0(src='assets/img/bg-masthead.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-xl-4.col-lg-5
                        .featured-text.text-center.text-lg-left
                            h4 Sistema Phi
                            p.text-black-50.mb-0
                                | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Suscipit minima excepturi nostrum beatae, reiciendis unde quaerat laudantium facere similique maiores nemo, esse porro magni consequuntur culpa ipsam voluptas fugit quae.
                // Project One Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-01.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
                                    h4.text-white Que Leo Concepción
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Veritatis possimus dolorum facilis magni distinctio quibusdam quasi voluptates, at quis saepe tenetur harum blanditiis inventore, sunt modi dignissimos. Dolor, quas illum?.
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.ml-0
                // Project Two Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-02.jpg', alt='')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
                                    h4.text-white Libreria Random
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fuga laudantium in maiores, laborum veritatis id reprehenderit aliquam quae expedita tempora quod explicabo voluptatem sunt quas consectetur exercitationem quia pariatur. Repudiandae?
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.mr-0

        // Signup
        section#signup.signup-section
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-10.col-lg-8.mx-auto.text-center
                        i.far.fa-paper-plane.fa-2x.mb-2.text-white
                        h2.text-white.mb-5 Suscríbete
                        form.form-inline.d-flex
                            input#inputEmail.form-control.flex-fill.mr-0.mr-sm-2.mb-3.mb-sm-0(type='email', placeholder='Ingresa tu Email')
                            button.btn.btn-primary.mx-auto(type='submit') Enviar

        // Contact
        section.contact-section.bg-black
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-map-marked-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Dirección
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50 Paicaví 128, Concepción
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-envelope.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Email
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50
                                    a(href='#!') sebastian@tausistemas.cl
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-mobile-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Teléfono
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50 +56 9 7664 6330
                .social.d-flex.justify-content-center
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-twitter
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-facebook-f
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-github

        // Footer
        footer.footer.bg-black.small.text-center.text-white-50
            .container
                | Copyright © Tausistemas 2020

